{"tid":1911190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再話去tvb同東方廣告商派嬲洗版冇用啦!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2020-03-05T07:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T23:33:37.000Z","uid":203685,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dccaa9cb44d40ff3a33fd14609c83878931384df","tid":1911190,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:22:46.000Z","msg":"連續兩次唔小心開左去吹水台 依家再開多次<br />\n<br />\n懶嘅直接睇最底紅字<br />\n<br />\n話說幾日前有依個post<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒 : 唔好再去建制Page俾嬲嬲 thx<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1901456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1901456</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多人睇完依個post 就叫人唔撚好去東方同cctvb嘅廣告商個到派嬲洗版<br />\n<br />\n但係 事實係咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iLq6Sf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiLq6Sf5.jpg&h=9f453859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該你地睇清楚啦 黃之鋒係叫你地唔好去<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建制Page</span></span>俾嬲嬲炸<br />\n<br />\n依家d廣告商嘅page 係唔撚係建制page呀<br />\n<br />\n我出左個post叫人抵制東方廣告商 屌老味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aFKjsPv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaFKjsPv.jpg&h=af9dae49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依個comment 都有348個正評 想問係咩事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府黑警民建聯唔怕核突，因為佢地唔駛向人民負責任；廣告商怕核突，因為消費者會令佢地負責任。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以後見到建制藍絲page 可以學黃之鋒講嘅咁做 但係唔該大家繼續去藍媒嘅廣告商派嬲洗版互like comment</span></span><br />\n<br />\nthx<br />\n<br />\nbtw 如果語氣重左 好對唔住 因為我真係好驚以後都冇人幫手抵制cctvb 同東方嘅廣告商"},{"pid":"4ae2df9f4b068b45b92804658fb6e7e9b9887b20","tid":1911190,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:23:33.000Z","msg":"睇完就做野啦<br />\n<br />\n【TVB任務，晒你幾秒】今日洗版精選 - 添寧，透濕能力差 (4 Mar)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1910258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.